

# MERN Authentication App

A simple MERN stack authentication project with:

- User registration (no auto-login)
- Login using JWT
- Protected dashboard
- Clean auth flow separation

## Folder Structure

backend/   – Node.js + Express API  
suraj/     – React frontend  

## Tech Stack

- React
- Node.js
- Express
- MongoDB
- JWT

## Setup Instructions

1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies in both frontend and backend
3. Create a `.env` file in backend with required variables
4. Run backend and frontend servers
